        },
        {
          "text": "Library is small not much students can study inside it",
          "name": "Shachi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "My college not held tournament in sports",
          "name": "Ayush sonkar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "And our classes frequency is very high etc",
          "name": "Ayush sonkar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "And our college parkspot some big to show your extra activities in front of student",
